thailand buy yugoslav crane in barter deal the cabinet approv a plan for the port author of thailand to buy six gantri crane from metalna co of yugoslavia for about 13.4 mln dlr , a govern spokesman said . he said thailand will pay for 25 pct of the cost of the crane in u.s. dlr and the rest by sale of rice , textil and other commod to yugoslavia . the bangkok shipown and agent associ ha appeal to the govern to scrap the purchas plan . it said it would be an unnecessari expens as most vessel call at the port alreadi have their own cargo handl equip .